<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Correa - Performance Wear</title>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Montserrat:wght@400;700;900&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>

body {
    margin: 0;
    font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif;
    background-color: #ffffff;
    color: #000;
}

header {
    padding: 30px;
    font-weight: 900;
    font-size: 24px;
    letter-spacing: 3px;
}

.hero {
    padding: 120px 20px;
    text-align: center;
}

.hero h1 {
    font-size: 50px;
    font-weight: 900;
}

.hero p {
    margin-top: 20px;
    font-size: 18px;
}

.button {
    display: inline-block;
    margin-top: 30px;
    padding: 15px 40px;
    background: black;
    color: white;
    text-decoration: none;
    font-weight: 700;
}

.products {
    padding: 80px 20px;
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(180px, 1fr));
    gap: 30px;
}

.product {
    text-align: center;
}

.product h3 {
    margin-top: 10px;
    font-size: 16px;
}

.color-box {
    height: 200px;
    background: #000;
}

.gray { background: #777; }
.white { background: #ddd; }
.green { background: #2f4f2f; }

footer {
    text-align: center;
    padding: 60px 20px;
    font-size: 14px;
}

</style>
</head>

<body>

<header>
CORREA
</header>

<section class="hero">
<h1>DISCIPLINA. INTENSIDAD. IDENTIDAD.</h1>
<p>Performance wear diseñada para entrenar sin límites.</p>
<a href="https://instagram.com/correa.urb" class="button">VER INSTAGRAM</a>
</section>

<section class="products">

<div class="product">
<div class="color-box"></div>
<h3>Sweat Guard - Negro</h3>
</div>

<div class="product">
<div class="color-box gray"></div>
<h3>Sweat Guard - Gris</h3>
</div>

<div class="product">
<div class="color-box white"></div>
<h3>Sweat Guard - Blanco</h3>
</div>

<div class="product">
<div class="color-box green"></div>
<h3>Sweat Guard - Verde</h3>
</div>

</section>

<footer>
Hecho para los que entrenan en serio.<br>
© 2026 CORREA
</footer>

</body>
</html>
